title: Oris Heritage - Oris Artelier Skeleton 30s HD 2014
description:
Oris Heritage - Oris Artelier Skeleton
A watch with inner beauty - This is the first skeleton watch within the Artelier line and it’s a beauty. The extra-large case opening permits an excellent view of the skeleton movement – and a fascinating opening into the world of mechanics. 

The dark-brown leather strap or stainless steel metal bracelet complete this art deco masterpiece of mechanical watches.

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of Oris Watches. Shop our full selection online, or in our store today!
